12 § 36.5. BOARD OF COMMISSIONERS,; COMPOSITION
13 (a) The administration, management, and supervision of the Authority shall
14 be vested in a Board of Commissioners, except as provided otherwise herein.
15 The Board shall consist of nine members, all of whom shall be residents of the
16 City of Rutland for their respective terms of office. One member of the Board
17 shall be the City Treasurer, and one member will be appointed from the Board
18 of Aldermen for a one year term. The remaining seven members of the Board
19 shall be appointed by the Mayor with the approval of the Board of Aldermen
20 pursuant to the charter of the City of Rutland. All members appointed except
21 for members appointed for creation of this Board shall serve for periods of
